WEBVTT

00:07.101 --> 00:10.921
(Perpetual Bloom)

00:11.401 --> 00:13.141
Marrying off your daughter
is a good thing.

00:13.601 --> 00:14.741
Why are you shedding tears?

00:15.641 --> 00:17.261
People will tease you for this.

00:20.641 --> 00:23.661
A daughter awaits a good husband
upon growing to adulthood,

00:24.161 --> 00:27.461
not knowing the pain of separation.

00:36.441 --> 00:38.341
Father, Fifth Uncle.

00:39.961 --> 00:41.101
Dou Zhao?

00:42.101 --> 00:43.241
Seventh Brother?

00:43.801 --> 00:45.421
How can we clean up this mess?

00:46.041 --> 00:47.621
Have you come up with a countermeasure?

00:48.981 --> 00:51.781
Shishu, why are you asking me this?

00:52.201 --> 00:53.850
I was kept in the dark too.

00:53.851 --> 00:55.280
I don't know what to do as well.

00:55.281 --> 00:56.661
Stop pretending.

00:56.921 --> 00:58.221
Do you think a lass like Ming

00:58.961 --> 01:01.141
could come up with
something like this by herself?

01:01.251 --> 01:02.231
What if Duke of Jining

01:02.241 --> 01:04.861
insists on blowing this issue up
and seeking the local authorities?

01:04.881 --> 01:07.061
The Dou family will
be embarrassed, you know?

01:07.921 --> 01:09.101
In my opinion,

01:09.481 --> 01:12.221
why don't we make the Wei Family

01:12.321 --> 01:14.000
acknowledge the marriage?

01:14.001 --> 01:15.581
We should keep this matter under wraps.

01:15.681 --> 01:17.480
This way, Ming won't suffer as much

01:17.481 --> 01:18.901
when she marries into the family.

01:18.961 --> 01:21.901
Ms. Longevity was supposed
to marry into their family.

01:21.961 --> 01:24.941
Isn't it reasonable for us to deliver more
dowries to them on Ming's behalf?

01:25.081 --> 01:27.641
How dare you still think about
touching Ms. Longevity's dowries?

01:27.921 --> 01:28.760
Tell me.

01:28.761 --> 01:30.141
Were you the one

01:30.241 --> 01:31.821
behind Ms. Longevity's switcheroo?

01:32.001 --> 01:33.740
I know you feel unfair
for Ms. Longevity.

01:33.741 --> 01:35.631
But Ming is our daughter as well.

01:35.641 --> 01:37.680
I gave birth to her
after ten months of pregnancy.

01:37.681 --> 01:39.421
Of course, I have to
give her my support.

01:39.721 --> 01:42.680
Do you expect me to stand idly by
as she takes her own life?

01:42.681 --> 01:44.791
How dare you still reason with me

01:44.801 --> 01:46.520
when you've done something
this shameful?

01:46.521 --> 01:48.451
In the end,
it's all because you spoiled her.

01:48.461 --> 01:50.320
How can you explain yourself
to Ms. Longevity?

01:50.321 --> 01:51.461
Enough.

01:51.881 --> 01:53.621
This is not the time
for a family argument.

01:53.941 --> 01:56.641
Ms. Longevity has the demeanor
of the eldest daughter in the family.

01:56.801 --> 01:58.240
Now, we should think about

01:58.241 --> 02:00.061
how to protect the family's reputation.

02:01.081 --> 02:03.920
Ms. Longevity, you should've told us
about their relationship earlier

02:03.921 --> 02:06.271
since you've realized their
affection for each other before.

02:06.281 --> 02:08.501
If so, it'll be easier
for us to re-plan the marriage.

02:08.511 --> 02:10.421
She's not willing
to be married to him anyway.

02:10.441 --> 02:11.701
Now, she has her wish granted.

02:12.001 --> 02:14.621
Besides, Ming was always meek.

02:14.881 --> 02:17.621
Why would she fall for Wei Tingyu
all of a sudden?

02:17.921 --> 02:20.541
Who knows if she
was instigated by someone?

02:22.121 --> 02:23.501
I'm already wounded.

02:23.781 --> 02:25.541
You guys didn't even hire
a physician for me

02:26.001 --> 02:27.661
in fear that people
might hear about this.

02:28.291 --> 02:30.221
Now that you want
to sweep things under the rug,

02:30.601 --> 02:32.461
you're actually pushing the blame on me?

02:33.121 --> 02:34.901
Look at the mess we're in now.

02:35.281 --> 02:36.411
I have no idea how to pacify

02:36.421 --> 02:38.381
Duchess of Jing tomorrow
if she confronts us.

02:38.391 --> 02:41.171
For now, the most urgent thing
is for you to draft a written agreement.

02:41.231 --> 02:42.821
State that you were sick for a long time

02:42.831 --> 02:44.280
and that it's hard
to bear children.

02:44.281 --> 02:46.021
You're withdrawing
from the marriage voluntarily

02:46.481 --> 02:48.681
due to fear of affecting
the lineage of the Wei Family.

02:49.081 --> 02:51.301
In the future, if the Wei Family
comes to confront us,

02:51.561 --> 02:53.061
we can use Ms. Longevity's dowries

02:53.401 --> 02:55.061
to make up for Ming's bluntness.

02:55.561 --> 02:58.261
After all, the Dou Family
was at fault first.

02:58.681 --> 03:01.981
This way, Ming can marry
into their family officially.

03:06.081 --> 03:07.861
Back then, you guys
forced me to get married

03:07.871 --> 03:09.021
when I didn't want to.

03:09.081 --> 03:11.861
You pressured me with talks
of parents' orders and family importance.

03:11.871 --> 03:13.181
Now that this has happened,

03:13.601 --> 03:15.621
you're forcing me
to be the victim again?

03:15.721 --> 03:17.941
If today's matter cannot be
resolved through discussion,

03:17.951 --> 03:20.011
I'll deliver the marriage certificate
to Shengtian tomorrow.

03:20.021 --> 03:21.901
I'll let the people
in the Capital be my judge.

03:21.911 --> 03:22.851
Have you lost your mind?

03:22.861 --> 03:23.800
This is preposterous.

03:23.801 --> 03:25.471
Do you have any regard
for the Dou Family?

03:25.481 --> 03:26.240
Shut up!

03:26.241 --> 03:27.381
That's enough!

03:30.401 --> 03:31.541
Shiying.

03:32.121 --> 03:33.040
You...

03:33.041 --> 03:35.221
You only care about
the Dou Family's reputation.

03:35.801 --> 03:37.741
My daughter is at fault
no matter what she does!

03:38.521 --> 03:39.801
You two even joined hands

03:39.811 --> 03:41.981
to force her to swallow
all her grievances in silence!

03:42.721 --> 03:43.901
She's my daughter!

03:44.041 --> 03:44.981
She's not your daughter!

03:44.991 --> 03:46.671
Even if the Wei family
demands an account,

03:46.681 --> 03:48.400
I, Dou Shiying,
will give them an account!

03:48.401 --> 03:50.261
You don't need to worry!

03:50.801 --> 03:51.941
And you,

03:53.281 --> 03:55.701
you've done such a shameful deed.

03:55.711 --> 03:57.181
You've ruined the family's reputation.

03:57.191 --> 03:59.461
And now, you're still thinking
of Ms. Longevity's dowries?

04:00.361 --> 04:02.021
You disgust me to no end!

04:03.841 --> 04:05.421
As an elder of the Dou family,

04:05.721 --> 04:07.741
you're acting as if
you care about the Dou family.

04:07.751 --> 04:09.811
But you only wish
to give the Wei family an account.

04:09.821 --> 04:11.881
Who will give Ms. Longevity
an account, then?

04:14.481 --> 04:15.320
Fine.

04:15.321 --> 04:16.861
I'll stay out of this!

04:16.921 --> 04:18.301
I don't need your interference!

04:20.841 --> 04:21.720
Ms. Longevity,

04:21.721 --> 04:22.861
let's go.

05:48.681 --> 05:52.800
=Blossom=
(Adapted from the novel "Blossom" by Zhi Zhi)

05:52.801 --> 05:56.021
=Episode 17=

05:56.681 --> 05:57.821
Does it still hurt?

05:58.041 --> 06:00.741
Do you need me to hire
an imperial physician for you?

06:02.041 --> 06:03.181
No need for that.

06:07.201 --> 06:09.741
Your fifth uncle always
looks at the bigger picture.

06:09.881 --> 06:12.191
Your mother had to swallow
a lot of grievances back then.

06:12.201 --> 06:15.381
This time, I mustn't let you
suffer the same fate.

06:16.281 --> 06:19.181
The incident may seem like
your stepmother's fault,

06:19.681 --> 06:20.861
but in reality,

06:21.681 --> 06:23.451
it's because your fifth uncle and I

06:23.461 --> 06:25.181
kept being lenient
to her all these years.

06:25.191 --> 06:27.381
That's why she's bold enough
to do something like that.

06:27.941 --> 06:30.581
You don't need to sign the
marriage certificate if you don't want.

06:30.841 --> 06:33.261
I'll join you if you want
to report her to the authorities.

06:33.281 --> 06:35.021
You don't need
to care about anything else.

06:35.241 --> 06:36.501
I'll cover your back.

06:37.121 --> 06:38.821
I'll punish your stepmother

06:38.841 --> 06:40.181
and make it up to you

06:40.761 --> 06:42.181
without showing any favoritism.

06:45.001 --> 06:47.141
It was an exhausting night.

06:48.761 --> 06:49.981
You should rest early.

06:56.961 --> 06:58.101
Father.

07:03.361 --> 07:04.981
Have you truly sobered up?

07:06.401 --> 07:07.541
That's right.

07:08.401 --> 07:09.901
I've sobered up.

07:10.261 --> 07:13.221
I won't get drunk again.

07:22.641 --> 07:26.381
(Serenity)

07:37.541 --> 07:40.401
Fourth Young Lady, are you really
going to report her to the authorities?

07:40.681 --> 07:42.021
I just said that out of spite.

07:42.801 --> 07:44.781
My head has been hurting the entire day.

07:45.241 --> 07:47.281
It's time to let Wang Yingxue
experience it herself.

07:52.041 --> 07:53.181
Dou Zhao.

07:56.481 --> 07:57.621
I'll marry you.

08:03.361 --> 08:04.501
Su Lan.

08:05.601 --> 08:07.421
Go buy me a bowl of tofu pudding.

08:09.081 --> 08:10.221
Yes, Fourth Young Lady.

08:19.241 --> 08:21.021
How did you know
that the bride wasn't me?

08:21.721 --> 08:22.941
I could tell at first glance

08:23.481 --> 08:24.741
that it wasn't you.

08:26.921 --> 08:28.061
Dou Zhao,

08:28.401 --> 08:29.621
marry me.

08:30.491 --> 08:32.661
Don't spend your days
suffering in a family like this.

08:33.441 --> 08:35.221
I'll treat you well in the future.

08:35.521 --> 08:37.621
No one will dare to bully you
again in the future.

08:38.121 --> 08:39.901
Do you think we're playing house here?

08:41.761 --> 08:43.461
Since Wei Tingyu married my sister,

08:43.841 --> 08:46.080
does that mean I have to find myself

08:46.081 --> 08:47.480
a husband who has a higher status,

08:47.481 --> 08:48.800
ranking, and is superior to him

08:48.801 --> 08:49.941
in all aspects?

08:51.081 --> 08:53.061
I just wish to lead my own life.

08:53.181 --> 08:54.941
There's no need
to pit myself against them.

08:55.081 --> 08:56.701
What about your own will, then?

08:58.001 --> 08:59.181
I don't wish to get married.

09:00.521 --> 09:01.661
Moreover,

09:02.761 --> 09:04.720
you and Fifth Uncle are sworn enemies.

09:04.721 --> 09:06.381
You and him are different.

09:06.601 --> 09:08.101
These are two different matters.

09:08.401 --> 09:09.541
For your sake,

09:09.661 --> 09:11.541
I might be able
to tolerate him a little more.

09:13.721 --> 09:15.341
I'm not saying this out of impulse.

09:16.321 --> 09:18.061
I'm more serious
than I've ever been before.

09:20.841 --> 09:22.101
I don't like you.

09:23.641 --> 09:25.261
That's why I cannot be married to you.

09:36.921 --> 09:38.061
You're lying.

09:40.601 --> 09:41.500
I'm not.

09:41.501 --> 09:42.981
That's not what I saw

09:44.001 --> 09:45.141
from your eyes.

09:57.601 --> 10:00.981
This is a magnolia tree,
my late mother's favorite plant.

10:09.201 --> 10:10.821
In the eighth year of the Chengping era,

10:12.281 --> 10:14.221
my mother took
her own life in front of me.

10:16.281 --> 10:18.221
My father had an affair
with Wang Yingxue.

10:18.641 --> 10:20.661
My mother's expectations of love

10:21.801 --> 10:23.661
(Perpetual Bloom)
shattered

10:24.841 --> 10:26.581
like brittle snow.

10:27.681 --> 10:29.560
The Dou Family even wanted
to frame my mother

10:29.561 --> 10:30.400
(Perpetual Bloom)

10:30.401 --> 10:31.741
by using the Seven Rules.

10:32.241 --> 10:33.381
They forced her to submit.

10:38.521 --> 10:41.821
No matter if it's love or marriage,

10:42.401 --> 10:44.021
I'm terrified of both.

10:46.081 --> 10:47.821
Your Lordship, I know you fancy me.

10:48.521 --> 10:49.821
I'm very grateful to you.

10:50.401 --> 10:51.541
It's just that...

10:52.401 --> 10:53.541
No wonder

10:54.401 --> 10:55.901
you rely on yourself for everything.

10:58.041 --> 10:59.421
But I can tell

11:02.721 --> 11:04.701
that this isn't all
of your true intentions.

11:06.401 --> 11:07.520
Fine.

11:07.521 --> 11:08.861
I'll tell you everything, then.

11:09.401 --> 11:11.140
I once had a strange dream.

11:11.141 --> 11:12.000
In my dream,

11:12.001 --> 11:14.360
both of us were killed
by the same arrow.

11:14.361 --> 11:15.200
If we continue

11:15.201 --> 11:16.720
to let our fates interact,

11:16.721 --> 11:17.861
I'm afraid...

11:19.481 --> 11:21.661
That's the reason you always feared me,

11:22.521 --> 11:23.661
right?

11:24.481 --> 11:26.221
I once had strange dreams too.

11:29.641 --> 11:31.221
But that was just a dream.

11:31.641 --> 11:33.861
No. It's more than just a dream.

11:34.241 --> 11:36.461
The mark behind my ear
is the best proof there is.

11:52.521 --> 11:55.661
But there's no red mark behind your ear.

12:00.281 --> 12:01.501
How could that be?

12:04.441 --> 12:05.741
It's actually gone?

12:06.081 --> 12:08.141
I knew you would cover it with rouge.

12:09.161 --> 12:10.301
But now,

12:10.921 --> 12:12.141
it's gone.

12:18.161 --> 12:19.501
If one day,

12:19.721 --> 12:22.261
with the power of towering mountains
and cascading valleys,

12:22.361 --> 12:25.080
you can make
this towering mountain before you

12:25.081 --> 12:26.401
collapse,

12:26.831 --> 12:30.501
the river will be changed.

12:31.251 --> 12:32.391
Dou Zhao.

12:37.321 --> 12:38.461
This is?

12:39.081 --> 12:40.261
This is the imperial decree.

12:42.201 --> 12:43.581
Since ancient times,

12:43.921 --> 12:46.181
countless women have
gone against their consciences

12:46.191 --> 12:47.741
and suffered for the rest of their lives

12:47.841 --> 12:49.480
because of their parents' orders.

12:49.481 --> 12:50.760
Prince Song is sincere.

12:50.761 --> 12:52.041
He's fighting for her happiness.

12:52.681 --> 12:53.821
Relay my order.

12:54.601 --> 12:56.181
For Fourth Young Lady Dou's marriage,

12:56.191 --> 12:58.361
there's no need to conform
to conventional etiquette.

12:58.371 --> 12:59.541
She can make her own decision.

13:00.481 --> 13:01.781
If the ceremony isn't completed,

13:02.121 --> 13:04.480
she may withdraw from her marriage
with Duke of Jining.

13:04.481 --> 13:06.640
(Imperial Bestowment)

13:06.641 --> 13:08.901
In the future, if anyone
forces you to get married again,

13:08.911 --> 13:09.941
you may show them this.

13:10.361 --> 13:11.501
You have the right to choose

13:11.601 --> 13:13.021
and refuse anyone you like.

13:13.281 --> 13:15.701
No matter if it's your father or uncle,

13:16.521 --> 13:18.261
no one can force you to do anything now.

13:20.321 --> 13:21.661
Although I believe

13:22.121 --> 13:24.501
that the purple crape myrtle
could grow independently,

13:26.801 --> 13:28.381
I believe that it would grow better

13:29.281 --> 13:30.861
if it receives support

13:31.761 --> 13:33.261
and love.

13:35.961 --> 13:37.541
You don't need to give me an answer now.

13:37.801 --> 13:39.781
Take your time to consider it.

13:40.241 --> 13:41.821
If you agree to my proposal,

13:42.321 --> 13:43.461
hang a red tassel

13:43.561 --> 13:44.560
on the magnolia tree

13:44.561 --> 13:46.101
in five days.

13:46.761 --> 13:48.381
I'll be able to see it from afar.

13:49.201 --> 13:50.341
If you refuse,

13:51.361 --> 13:52.621
hang a white tassel on it.

13:54.161 --> 13:55.301
In the future,

13:56.961 --> 13:58.661
I shall not bother you again.

14:01.041 --> 14:02.181
Farewell.

14:12.401 --> 14:15.461
(Duke of Jining's Residence)

14:28.251 --> 14:29.930
Last night was their wedding night.

14:29.931 --> 14:32.411
It's normal for them
to wake up late the next day.

14:39.961 --> 14:41.101
Tingzhen...

14:41.521 --> 14:42.661
What's wrong?

14:45.841 --> 14:46.680
Come out.

14:46.681 --> 14:47.901
I have something to tell you.

14:48.401 --> 14:50.480
You can tell me right here.

14:50.481 --> 14:51.520
I...

14:51.521 --> 14:52.701
Tell me.

15:10.151 --> 15:11.781
What are you doing here?

15:12.841 --> 15:14.901
How dare the Dou Family do such a thing?

15:15.121 --> 15:16.560
(Aspire for Greatness)
My brother

15:16.561 --> 15:18.240
drank quite a lot last night.

15:18.241 --> 15:19.501
He has a headache.

15:19.661 --> 15:21.240
Madam Wei, if you have something to say,

15:21.241 --> 15:23.581
you may discuss it with me and Yingxue.

15:25.101 --> 15:28.021
What's there to discuss when you guys have
deceived us with a switcheroo?

15:29.201 --> 15:30.661
We're a family.

15:30.841 --> 15:31.981
You don't need to do this.

15:32.321 --> 15:34.101
Who said she was a part of my family?

15:34.111 --> 15:36.001
Her name isn't even
on the marriage certificate!

15:36.881 --> 15:40.141
If I send this to Shengtian,
this can be used as a proof of crime!

15:44.721 --> 15:45.861
Mother.

15:49.241 --> 15:52.021
Since we've already done the deed,

15:52.321 --> 15:53.461
we should confess.

15:54.121 --> 15:55.261
As the saying goes,

15:55.601 --> 15:57.781
wrong palanquin, right man.

15:58.241 --> 16:00.480
As long as the youngsters
are happy with it,

16:00.481 --> 16:02.360
I guess it's acceptable

16:02.361 --> 16:03.981
to break some old conventions

16:04.121 --> 16:05.621
if it makes them happy.

16:05.681 --> 16:06.520
Madam Wang,

16:06.521 --> 16:09.061
your father is the Minister of War.

16:09.241 --> 16:11.101
Now, Fifth Master Dou is backing you up.

16:11.521 --> 16:13.981
Are you trying to rewrite the law here?

16:14.321 --> 16:18.661
Deceiving the court with a substitution
in marriage is punishable by flogging.

16:18.681 --> 16:21.181
Madam Wei, if you do intend
to report this to the authorities,

16:21.201 --> 16:24.221
you should be at Shengtian
at this moment.

16:24.601 --> 16:26.461
What are you doing
at the Dou's Residence now?

16:26.471 --> 16:28.331
The wedding banquet
has already been completed.

16:28.341 --> 16:29.901
If you file a lawsuit now,

16:30.401 --> 16:32.600
it'll only result
in the embarrassment and humiliation

16:32.601 --> 16:34.901
of both families.

16:35.161 --> 16:36.781
Madam Wei, why don't you

16:36.961 --> 16:38.501
just tell us about your intention?

16:40.001 --> 16:41.821
This marriage doesn't count.

16:42.281 --> 16:43.480
Return the betrothal gifts

16:43.481 --> 16:45.421
we gave you threefold,

16:45.441 --> 16:47.061
and I'll forget about this incident.

16:49.081 --> 16:50.941
So, in the end,
all you care about is money.

16:51.401 --> 16:53.480
But you want threefold? Isn't it...

16:53.481 --> 16:55.181
No matter how greedy a person is,

16:55.441 --> 16:57.501
they could never demand
a compensation of this sum.

16:57.891 --> 16:59.000
Do you think the Dou Family

16:59.001 --> 17:00.581
receives a windfall from time to time?

17:00.601 --> 17:02.181
You can go ahead and do what you want.

17:02.401 --> 17:04.101
Do you think Duke of Jining

17:04.321 --> 17:07.021
did not consummate with my daughter?

17:07.181 --> 17:09.261
You really have the nerve
to cause a scene here, huh?

17:10.921 --> 17:12.701
If Shengtian cannot handle this,

17:12.921 --> 17:13.920
I'll tell His Majesty

17:13.921 --> 17:15.781
and Her Majesty to handle this case!

17:17.481 --> 17:18.621
Tingzhen.

17:24.041 --> 17:25.360
Heaven and Earth, be my witness!

17:25.361 --> 17:27.821
This is all my fault alone!

17:28.221 --> 17:29.461
It has nothing to do with Ming.

17:30.731 --> 17:31.600
Strange.

17:31.601 --> 17:34.101
Even a cowardly turtle has its moments
of stepping up, huh?

17:34.121 --> 17:36.781
I was the one who persuaded Ming
to proceed with the switcheroo.

17:37.421 --> 17:39.201
No matter if
it's compensation or punishment,

17:39.211 --> 17:40.661
I, Wei Tingyu alone, will bear them.

17:40.761 --> 17:42.301
I'll say the same thing

17:42.321 --> 17:43.581
even if His Majesty is here.

17:43.821 --> 17:45.461
(Marriage Certificate)
What a load of nonsense!

17:45.481 --> 17:46.840
They were at fault from the start!

17:46.841 --> 17:48.361
Why are you trying to bear the blame?

17:49.041 --> 17:49.880
Excellent!

17:49.881 --> 17:51.881
This is an action befitting
of the Duke of Jining.

18:06.801 --> 18:08.261
I promised I would watch over you.

18:08.521 --> 18:09.661
I'll keep my promise.

18:11.441 --> 18:13.741
Ming and I truly love each other.

18:13.881 --> 18:15.061
I don't need a single cent

18:15.161 --> 18:16.421
from the Dou Family.

18:17.621 --> 18:20.661
I only hope that the elders of both
families can renew the marriage contract

18:20.671 --> 18:22.741
to give Ming and me a rightful status.

18:26.481 --> 18:29.061
Dou, if you do love me,

18:29.561 --> 18:31.101
can you carry me on your back

18:31.721 --> 18:32.981
and walk a few rounds

18:33.161 --> 18:36.541
after you bring me to your residence?

18:37.041 --> 18:38.381
I will do it.

18:43.241 --> 18:44.501
Since it has come to this,

18:45.041 --> 18:46.421
it should be so.

18:46.881 --> 18:49.301
You're being stubborn again, huh?

18:49.361 --> 18:50.560
All these years of education

18:50.561 --> 18:51.971
and rite-learning were for nothing!

18:52.321 --> 18:53.941
If you get yourself a wife like this,

18:53.961 --> 18:55.901
people will mock you forever!

18:55.911 --> 18:57.200
I'll lead my own life.

18:57.201 --> 18:58.501
They can mock me all they like.

18:59.201 --> 19:00.421
I've already deemed her

19:00.481 --> 19:01.821
as my wife.

19:08.361 --> 19:10.941
Madam Wei, what do you think
about your marriage?

19:12.321 --> 19:13.941
Stop your nonsense!

19:24.441 --> 19:26.701
When I was her age,

19:27.801 --> 19:31.101
I have always hoped that in this life,

19:31.481 --> 19:33.821
there would be someone who would
protect me and love me.

19:37.481 --> 19:40.501
But it's impossible to have that
in this lifetime.

19:42.801 --> 19:44.101
But there's still hope

19:45.121 --> 19:46.341
for the youngsters.

19:50.171 --> 19:51.311
Madam Wei,

19:51.961 --> 19:54.101
do you still remember the promise
we made at Duanyang?

19:55.441 --> 19:56.661
Please leave.

20:13.241 --> 20:14.240
Father,

20:14.241 --> 20:15.941
I've let Zhao down.

20:16.201 --> 20:18.101
I'll apologize to Zhao right now.

20:18.241 --> 20:19.240
No.

20:19.241 --> 20:20.621
I've let Fourth Lady down.

20:21.361 --> 20:22.741
I'll beg her for forgiveness.

20:30.121 --> 20:32.861
Fifth Young Lady and Wei Tingyu
are heading to our courtyard.

20:33.041 --> 20:35.360
Young Lady, it's like Wei Tingyu
has changed entirely.

20:35.361 --> 20:36.320
He's become responsible.

20:36.321 --> 20:38.001
He said he came here
to apologize to you.

20:38.211 --> 20:39.971
I couldn't care less.

20:40.321 --> 20:41.461
Come here quickly.

20:41.801 --> 20:44.200
- Look at the red mark behind my ear.
- Young Lady.

20:44.201 --> 20:45.881
Has it truly disappeared?

20:45.891 --> 20:47.611
You've been looking at it
for the entire afternoon.

20:47.621 --> 20:48.741
You should have some water.

20:50.521 --> 20:51.661
By the way, Miss,

20:51.781 --> 20:53.760
Wang Yingxue has dragged
Madam Wei into the room.

20:53.761 --> 20:55.141
They're being so mysterious.

20:55.361 --> 20:57.181
Why are they being so secretive?

20:58.261 --> 21:00.541
Everything in the world
is driven by the pursuit of gain.

21:01.121 --> 21:03.261
At the moment, there seems
to be no better option

21:03.721 --> 21:05.661
than sharing the profits
with Wei Tingzhen.

21:15.391 --> 21:17.021
(Ledger)
This is all of my usury business

21:17.171 --> 21:19.181
in the Capital.

21:19.341 --> 21:22.520
The related government offices are all
waiting to curry favor with my father.

21:22.521 --> 21:24.101
Adding one more point of interest

21:24.521 --> 21:25.981
won't cut off the flow of wealth.

21:27.521 --> 21:29.421
As long as you leave
your thumbprint here,

21:29.561 --> 21:31.021
half of the dividends

21:31.561 --> 21:34.941
will be delivered to your residence
by different money houses

21:35.201 --> 21:37.341
every month on time.

21:37.521 --> 21:40.381
Madam Wang,
you're straightforward indeed.

21:46.241 --> 21:47.741
Regarding the marriage certificate,

21:48.281 --> 21:50.421
let's pick an auspicious hour
together tomorrow.

21:50.601 --> 21:52.341
I'll call the duke of our residence

21:52.641 --> 21:54.760
and several lords from
the Imperial Clan Court

21:54.761 --> 21:56.640
to be our witnesses.

21:56.641 --> 21:59.280
That will surely put an end
to the idle gossip.

21:59.281 --> 22:00.360
Don't worry.

22:00.361 --> 22:02.960
She'll be my sister-in-law
in the future.

22:02.961 --> 22:04.741
I'll treat her well.

22:07.041 --> 22:08.821
Madam Wei, thank you for your effort.

22:14.001 --> 22:14.840
Ming,

22:14.841 --> 22:16.341
if you don't know what to say later,

22:16.641 --> 22:17.821
I'll apologize to her first.

22:24.141 --> 22:26.040
Your Lordship, Fifth Young Lady,
please return.

22:26.041 --> 22:27.581
Miss doesn't want to see anyone.

22:33.561 --> 22:34.480
Zhao,

22:34.481 --> 22:36.021
I've let you down.

22:36.081 --> 22:37.551
(Perpetual Bloom)
Fourth Young Lady,

22:37.561 --> 22:40.311
Ming only came up with that terrible
method because she was desperate.

22:40.321 --> 22:41.381
She has broken your heart.

22:41.421 --> 22:42.560
If you want to blame someone,

22:42.561 --> 22:43.701
you should blame me.

22:43.961 --> 22:45.301
How is she brokenhearted?

22:45.481 --> 22:47.360
His Lordship fancies Young Lady.

22:47.361 --> 22:48.941
She doesn't have time for them.

22:50.361 --> 22:53.141
Fourth Young Lady,
we've owed you too much.

22:53.801 --> 22:55.261
In the future, just tell me

22:55.361 --> 22:57.101
if you need any help

22:57.241 --> 22:58.461
in the future.

22:58.801 --> 23:01.261
I, Wei Tingyu, will surely do my best

23:01.601 --> 23:03.461
to repay your huge favor.

23:16.321 --> 23:18.381
(Even a cold and unfeeling person
like Wei Tingyu)

23:18.841 --> 23:20.901
(is treating Dou Ming sincerely.)

23:21.961 --> 23:26.021
(Maybe they're destined to be together.)

23:34.201 --> 23:35.821
Here are 5,000 silver taels banknote.

23:36.521 --> 23:37.661
Keep them.

23:38.321 --> 23:39.461
Father.

23:39.721 --> 23:40.861
I know.

23:41.361 --> 23:42.981
I know that money alone

23:43.221 --> 23:45.301
cannot atone for all the sins
that I've committed.

23:47.201 --> 23:48.981
But I don't know
what else I can do for you

23:49.281 --> 23:51.621
besides giving you money.

23:52.481 --> 23:56.261
When you were born,
I promised your mother

23:56.361 --> 23:58.381
that I would do my best
to treat you well

23:59.001 --> 24:01.541
and make you happy.

24:02.641 --> 24:05.141
When you were young,
you kept clinging to me.

24:05.721 --> 24:07.461
You would always hang on my neck

24:07.641 --> 24:09.741
whenever I was studying
or entertaining officials.

24:10.641 --> 24:11.781
But,

24:12.881 --> 24:14.861
ever since Guqiu's passing,

24:17.121 --> 24:18.861
I felt like you were
no longer close to me.

24:21.561 --> 24:23.541
Whenever I returned
to the manor to visit you...

24:23.841 --> 24:24.981
Grandmother,

24:25.231 --> 24:25.871
what is this?

24:25.881 --> 24:28.341
Ms. Longevity and I made these
lotus root dumplings together.

24:28.351 --> 24:29.371
But we weren't good at it.

24:29.381 --> 24:30.861
They became sticky after cooking.

24:30.961 --> 24:33.261
Come. Let me try.

24:35.681 --> 24:36.821
What do you think?

24:38.121 --> 24:41.261
The lotus root dumpling paste
tastes better than the dumplings.

24:42.041 --> 24:43.040
Master,

24:43.041 --> 24:45.080
- why do you never go inside?
- Guys, try it.

24:45.081 --> 24:46.221
Take your seats.

24:46.761 --> 24:48.331
Initially, I thought

24:48.761 --> 24:51.731
they would have a hard time
after leaving me.

24:52.321 --> 24:54.041
But seeing how happy they look

24:54.321 --> 24:55.621
made me realize

24:56.321 --> 24:58.441
that I was
the extra member of the house.

25:04.401 --> 25:05.541
Father,

25:05.961 --> 25:07.581
I don't need your money.

25:08.521 --> 25:11.141
But I hope that you can
agree to this request of mine.

25:12.641 --> 25:14.941
If anyone wants to discuss marriage
with me again,

25:15.081 --> 25:16.701
reject all of them.

25:17.481 --> 25:18.621
Ms. Longevity.

25:20.041 --> 25:22.101
You still have a long way to go.

25:23.121 --> 25:25.261
Don't punish yourself
because of the foolish mistake

25:25.681 --> 25:27.261
I did in the past.

25:28.461 --> 25:31.001
Entrusting your life to the wrong person
is the worst punishment.

25:31.681 --> 25:35.120
Moreover, I have Grandmother,
I have you, and I have my friends.

25:35.121 --> 25:36.491
I own a business too.

25:36.821 --> 25:38.501
And, there are many

25:38.961 --> 25:41.501
magical and mysterious things
in the world

25:41.921 --> 25:43.821
that are worth learning from.

25:44.001 --> 25:46.061
That's the life I want to lead.

25:46.201 --> 25:47.941
It's not
that I don't want to get married.

25:48.221 --> 25:50.341
I just don't want
to be married to the wrong person.

25:53.561 --> 25:54.821
I promise you.

25:55.001 --> 25:56.381
In the future, you can decide

25:56.641 --> 25:58.221
your own marriage.

26:00.401 --> 26:01.541
Thank you, Father.

26:03.881 --> 26:05.541
There's one more thing.

26:06.001 --> 26:07.701
It's related to Wang Yingxue.

26:09.921 --> 26:11.221
What's wrong with her again?

26:14.241 --> 26:16.541
(Willow Alley, To Miss Wang)

26:16.581 --> 26:18.061
(To Yingxue, Under the Moonlit Night)

26:24.281 --> 26:25.421
Dou.

26:26.201 --> 26:26.951
In the future,

26:26.961 --> 26:29.671
you should hand our domestic affairs
and accounts to Ms. Longevity.

26:34.121 --> 26:36.181
Right after Ming's crisis was resolved,

26:37.321 --> 26:39.301
you're in a hurry
to go for the kill, huh?

26:45.321 --> 26:47.701
When Wei Tingyu was reciting
his touching vows,

26:49.561 --> 26:51.341
weren't you reminded of

26:51.961 --> 26:54.261
the promises you made to me?

26:58.601 --> 27:02.101
I still have the poems and letters

27:03.121 --> 27:04.621
you wrote to me.

27:10.961 --> 27:12.101
Fine.

27:14.081 --> 27:16.061
Let's get to business, then.

27:16.401 --> 27:17.541
Usually,

27:17.681 --> 27:20.421
who takes care of the unpaid taxes

27:21.041 --> 27:22.920
owed by those nobles and officials?

27:22.921 --> 27:25.701
And when you can't
account for the missing records,

27:25.781 --> 27:28.301
who goes door to door,
begging tirelessly?

27:28.641 --> 27:31.381
It was me, Wang Yingxue.

27:31.481 --> 27:33.461
Why should I hand both of them to her?

27:35.041 --> 27:36.181
Do you think

27:36.401 --> 27:38.501
tomorrow's sun cannot rise without you?

27:39.401 --> 27:40.720
Even if I lose you,

27:40.721 --> 27:42.301
I can still live normally.

27:42.801 --> 27:44.181
Madam's abilities

27:44.901 --> 27:46.981
are way beyond than
handling the family's accounts.

27:47.301 --> 27:50.041
If not, how could she persuade
Madam Wei to agree to the marriage?

27:50.201 --> 27:51.861
Even Ms. Longevity could tell.

27:52.241 --> 27:53.861
Who are you still trying to deceive?

27:54.361 --> 27:56.840
Lending money at a high interest
is a serious crime.

27:56.841 --> 27:58.741
The Dou Family will fall
because of your crime!

28:00.361 --> 28:01.501
I didn't do it.

28:02.001 --> 28:03.040
I didn't!

28:03.041 --> 28:04.541
She's framing me!

28:05.141 --> 28:05.891
Gao Sheng overheard

28:05.901 --> 28:07.880
your conversation with
Wei Tingzhen in the room.

28:07.881 --> 28:09.141
How dare you still deny it?

28:09.841 --> 28:11.000
All these years,

28:11.001 --> 28:13.521
you did maintain a perfect front
when it came to our accounts.

28:13.661 --> 28:16.021
I thought you actually devoted
yourself to the family.

28:16.201 --> 28:17.781
I never expected you to do this.

28:19.081 --> 28:20.701
Let's go and see your father now.

28:20.941 --> 28:22.930
Let's tell him to investigate
how his own daughter

28:22.931 --> 28:24.720
is undermining him!

28:24.721 --> 28:25.840
No!

28:25.841 --> 28:28.520
Shiying, I know my fault now!

28:28.521 --> 28:29.981
I truly know my fault now!

28:30.501 --> 28:32.061
You mustn't tell my father about this!

28:32.561 --> 28:33.520
No!

28:33.521 --> 28:35.301
You mustn't tell anyone about this!

28:35.521 --> 28:37.960
I've spent all the dirty money

28:37.961 --> 28:39.901
on the Dou Family!

28:42.941 --> 28:44.221
Fifth Brother knows about this!

28:44.621 --> 28:45.960
Fifth Brother knows everything!

28:45.961 --> 28:48.261
Dou, let's ask Fifth Brother about this!

28:49.201 --> 28:51.481
Stay in the side courtyard
and reflect upon your mistakes!

28:51.521 --> 28:53.901
From now on, Ms. Longevity shall
handle the household.

28:53.921 --> 28:56.531
Not a single dirty coin must ever
flow into the Dou Family again.

29:09.921 --> 29:10.960
(Dou's Residence)

29:10.961 --> 29:12.560
- Open the door!
- Open the door!

29:12.561 --> 29:13.880
- Open the door!
- Open the door!

29:13.881 --> 29:15.480
- Open the door!
- Open the door for us!

29:15.481 --> 29:16.330
Open the door!

29:16.331 --> 29:17.380
Open the door!

29:17.381 --> 29:18.470
- Open the door!
- Open the door!

29:18.471 --> 29:20.301
(Orchid's Fragrance Highlights Serenity)

29:20.731 --> 29:21.951
Open the door!

29:23.401 --> 29:25.101
It's so early in the morning.

29:25.361 --> 29:27.461
Where did all the quacking come from?

29:27.881 --> 29:29.240
Guys, please calm down!

29:29.241 --> 29:31.701
Stop fighting!

29:33.011 --> 29:33.920
Calm down!

29:33.921 --> 29:35.061
Everyone, calm down!

29:38.001 --> 29:38.891
No!

29:38.901 --> 29:41.000
I will absolutely not accept
the wild geese as gifts.

29:41.001 --> 29:43.120
Guys, please return.

29:43.121 --> 29:44.911
This is Lord Qing's
letter of recommendation.

29:46.401 --> 29:48.181
I serve the crown prince, you know?

29:48.521 --> 29:50.480
I, Guo Yan, am peers

29:50.481 --> 29:52.231
with Seventh Master Dou
in Neo-Confucianism.

29:52.241 --> 29:53.240
Fate has brought us together.

29:53.241 --> 29:54.631
I've been a widower for many years.

29:54.641 --> 29:57.800
Coincidentally, Fourth Young Lady Dou
is not that young as well.

29:57.801 --> 30:00.901
Fourth Young Lady Dou is
at least 20 years younger than you.

30:00.961 --> 30:03.701
Lord Guo, I don't think you studied
Neo-Confucianism.

30:04.081 --> 30:05.221
In my opinion,

30:05.441 --> 30:08.821
I think you studied
how to get yourself a young wife.

30:09.001 --> 30:10.141
You!

30:10.561 --> 30:11.901
I'm no match for you.

30:12.041 --> 30:13.081
You're young and talented.

30:13.091 --> 30:14.851
You've already
given birth to many children

30:14.861 --> 30:16.240
without getting an official wife.

30:16.241 --> 30:17.211
What do you mean by that?

30:17.221 --> 30:18.120
So what?

30:18.121 --> 30:19.160
What did you say?

30:19.161 --> 30:20.080
To hell with you!

30:20.081 --> 30:21.861
- So what?
- How dare you hit me?

30:23.371 --> 30:24.280
I'll kill you!

30:24.281 --> 30:25.421
It's you!

30:25.521 --> 30:26.400
Master,

30:26.401 --> 30:27.661
Lord Liang is paying us a visit.

30:29.201 --> 30:30.341
Hurry and invite him.

30:30.381 --> 30:32.800
Everyone, I have to handle
the Ministry of Revenue's affairs.

30:32.801 --> 30:33.810
Lord Liang is looking for me.

30:33.811 --> 30:35.391
I'm sure he has something important
to discuss.

30:35.401 --> 30:36.080
Farewell.

30:36.081 --> 30:37.221
Sorry about this.

30:37.401 --> 30:39.871
- Lord Dou, take the proposal!
- Lord Dou, take the proposal!

30:40.161 --> 30:41.301
It's all your fault!

30:42.521 --> 30:43.661
Lord Liang.

30:43.761 --> 30:44.901
Shiying.

30:44.911 --> 30:46.280
It's about time for my fourth son

30:46.281 --> 30:48.501
to get married.

30:48.601 --> 30:49.741
You...

30:53.481 --> 30:54.560
This is bad.

30:54.561 --> 30:56.101
I'm afraid I'm having a headache again.

30:56.121 --> 30:57.741
Farewell.

30:57.841 --> 30:58.981
Farewell.

31:06.321 --> 31:07.461
Here.

31:10.801 --> 31:12.141
Bear with it.

31:13.801 --> 31:14.941
It's fine.

31:15.181 --> 31:16.321
It doesn't hurt.

31:16.681 --> 31:17.821
I feel much better now.

31:20.561 --> 31:22.691
Master, all those geese are
still in the courtyard.

31:22.701 --> 31:23.741
How should we deal with them?

31:23.751 --> 31:24.791
Throw them outside.

31:25.201 --> 31:27.221
I panic when I think about

31:27.321 --> 31:28.541
all those livestock.

31:28.721 --> 31:30.901
It'll be humiliating
if you throw them away.

31:33.001 --> 31:35.221
You should return them
back at night sneakily.

31:35.321 --> 31:36.461
All right.

31:39.101 --> 31:40.971
Since the substitution marriage
had happened,

31:42.001 --> 31:43.560
they came to the Dou Family

31:43.561 --> 31:45.221
to take advantage of the situation.

31:45.381 --> 31:47.270
Why should we show them any respect?

31:47.271 --> 31:48.901
They're crooks.

31:49.041 --> 31:50.901
There's no need to be angry at them.

31:52.681 --> 31:55.061
Initially, I've made you some goose soup

31:55.401 --> 31:57.101
to help relieve heatiness.

31:57.141 --> 31:58.400
But when I think about the fact

31:58.401 --> 32:00.741
that the goose
has a sharp beak and wings,

32:01.121 --> 32:02.640
I think I should order the kitchen

32:02.641 --> 32:03.640
to make something else.

32:03.641 --> 32:04.640
Don't.

32:04.641 --> 32:07.421
Ms. Longevity, it'll definitely work
since you made it.

32:20.231 --> 32:21.280
Did you scald your tongue?

32:21.281 --> 32:22.541
I'm fine.

32:23.121 --> 32:24.301
It's delicious.

32:30.311 --> 32:31.671
This time, you don't need to worry.

32:33.361 --> 32:34.880
I'll send every single one of them back

32:34.881 --> 32:36.661
even if there are 100 geese
in the residence.

32:37.921 --> 32:39.061
Drink it slowly.

32:44.361 --> 32:45.360
Master,

32:45.361 --> 32:48.221
Earl of Haichang is here to ask
for Fourth Young Lady's hand.

32:50.001 --> 32:51.221
Earl of Haichang?

32:55.801 --> 32:58.541
You mean the one who has
slept 3,000 prostitutes in the Capital?

32:59.241 --> 33:00.720
He's killing me!

33:00.721 --> 33:02.511
- Don't run! I'll kill you!
- He's beating me up!

33:02.521 --> 33:04.200
- Master!
- I'll beat you to death!

33:04.201 --> 33:05.320
- I'll beat you to death!
- Master!

33:05.321 --> 33:06.440
Master, calm down!

33:06.441 --> 33:07.760
Master, don't be angry!

33:07.761 --> 33:09.071
- Please be appeased!
- Go away!

33:09.081 --> 33:10.091
You scum!

33:10.101 --> 33:11.320
How dare you ask for her hand?

33:11.321 --> 33:13.080
Do you think my residence is a brothel?

33:13.081 --> 33:15.131
Seventh Master Dou,
what has gotten into you?

33:15.141 --> 33:16.640
Since no one wants
Fourth Young Lady,

33:16.641 --> 33:17.631
I'm willing to marry her!

33:17.641 --> 33:18.720
I'm doing you a favor.

33:18.721 --> 33:19.720
You shameless scum!

33:19.721 --> 33:20.800
I'll beat you to death!

33:20.801 --> 33:21.860
- Help!
- Master!

33:21.861 --> 33:23.080
- I'll beat you to death!
- What's with the ruckus?

33:23.081 --> 33:25.041
- Stop right there!
- Master, please be appeased!

33:25.201 --> 33:27.080
Seventh Master Dou is beating me!

33:27.081 --> 33:28.221
Stop running!

33:28.681 --> 33:31.741
- Master!
- He's beating me!

33:31.881 --> 33:33.501
- Hurry!
- Master!

33:34.361 --> 33:35.701
What has gotten into you?

33:35.961 --> 33:37.251
Scaring him is fine.

33:37.261 --> 33:39.560
Earl of Haichang comes from
a family of nobles, you know?

33:39.561 --> 33:41.120
How could you hit him for real?

33:41.121 --> 33:44.261
All those shameless scums
are trying to marry Ms. Longevity.

33:44.521 --> 33:46.341
They deserved the beating.

33:46.521 --> 33:47.661
You...

33:48.401 --> 33:50.261
Father, you were implicated
because of me.

33:50.801 --> 33:53.271
You think that you're free
after withdrawing from the marriage.

33:53.281 --> 33:54.621
We arrange a marriage for you

33:54.681 --> 33:56.181
so that we can at least protect you.

33:56.441 --> 33:57.981
You'll know how terrifying it is

33:58.001 --> 33:59.861
when outsiders plot against you.

34:01.441 --> 34:02.581
Forget it.

34:03.121 --> 34:04.871
You missed Grandmother, right?

34:04.881 --> 34:07.061
You can return to the manor
and lay low for the moment.

34:07.261 --> 34:10.141
Let the Dou's Residence
have some peace and quiet for now.

34:11.041 --> 34:12.181
Understood.

34:13.401 --> 34:15.160
Earl of Guangen? Earl of Changyu?

34:15.161 --> 34:16.720
They're a bunch of scums.

34:16.721 --> 34:18.160
They're even worse than Wei Tingyu.

34:18.161 --> 34:20.481
Everyone in Zhending Market
knows who I am.

34:20.491 --> 34:21.720
How dare they bully my sister?

34:21.721 --> 34:23.741
I'll slaughter them
with my men tomorrow.

34:26.881 --> 34:30.181
Your fifth uncle is also a lord now.

34:30.801 --> 34:33.341
But he has to chase you away
to make peace with them.

34:34.741 --> 34:36.141
It's good that he's chasing me away.

34:36.321 --> 34:38.541
It's best that he doesn't call me
to return ever again.

34:40.761 --> 34:42.621
Times have changed.

34:43.001 --> 34:45.461
The Dou Family
is the new favorite in the court.

34:45.691 --> 34:47.621
Now that I look at it,
your fifth uncle might be

34:47.681 --> 34:49.821
the next Grand Secretary.

34:50.681 --> 34:53.341
All those officials he wanted
to butter up in the past

34:53.481 --> 34:55.381
have the same rank as him now.

34:55.761 --> 34:59.541
Now, they're trying
to butter him up instead.

34:59.641 --> 35:02.181
Fifth Uncle has power
while Father has money.

35:02.401 --> 35:04.541
And, a substitution marriage
has occurred.

35:05.081 --> 35:06.381
To outsiders,

35:06.401 --> 35:08.421
I'm a huge bargain up for grabs.

35:10.401 --> 35:14.061
Shiying has finally done
something heroic this time.

35:14.281 --> 35:16.640
When you look at the smaller picture,

35:16.641 --> 35:18.421
it's just a marriage.

35:18.821 --> 35:20.400
But when you look at the bigger picture,

35:20.401 --> 35:23.861
it's a case of the Dou Family choosing
between the crown prince and Lord Qing.

35:26.801 --> 35:29.120
Now, everyone in the imperial court

35:29.121 --> 35:31.541
will make their choice
based on our choice.

35:32.041 --> 35:33.520
Maybe His Majesty

35:33.521 --> 35:36.661
is also waiting to see our stand.

35:37.561 --> 35:38.941
If so, we won't choose any of them.

35:40.841 --> 35:42.261
It's good to take a step back.

35:43.081 --> 35:46.581
It's better to act
after understanding the situation.

35:47.921 --> 35:50.541
You guys are discussing the marriage
as if it's war.

35:50.641 --> 35:53.760
If His Majesty is that free,
we can do another substitution marriage.

35:53.761 --> 35:55.161
I'll go on Ms. Longevity's behalf.

35:57.801 --> 35:58.920
Grandmother,

35:58.921 --> 36:00.760
the raisins are sweet.

36:00.761 --> 36:01.901
You should try them.

36:05.761 --> 36:06.640
It's sweet, right?

36:06.641 --> 36:09.320
- (Grandmother is healthy and happy.)
- Try this.

36:09.321 --> 36:10.480
Try this.

36:10.481 --> 36:12.661
(Everything is developing
in a good direction.)

36:26.641 --> 36:27.780
Young Lady, Old Madam,

36:27.781 --> 36:28.941
here's the tofu pudding.

36:29.761 --> 36:30.901
Tofu pudding?

36:47.321 --> 36:48.701
It tastes like Lin's tofu pudding.

36:49.041 --> 36:50.261
And, it's still warm.

36:53.441 --> 36:54.581
Lin's?

36:55.121 --> 36:57.120
I thought they were
located in the Capital.

36:57.121 --> 36:58.381
Where did they come from?

36:58.921 --> 37:00.341
Lu Ming delivered them to us.

37:04.441 --> 37:06.661
(Tea)

37:19.781 --> 37:22.080
Why are we practicing
how to make tofu pudding every day?

37:22.081 --> 37:23.111
Cut the crap.

37:23.121 --> 37:25.240
Our lord said that one must travel
1,000 li with the tofu pudding intact

37:25.241 --> 37:27.051
if they wish to achieve
mastery in equestrian.

37:27.061 --> 37:28.640
Practicing our next move is key.

37:28.641 --> 37:29.781
- Yes, sir!
- Yes, sir!

37:30.601 --> 37:31.520
Your Lordship,

37:31.521 --> 37:32.360
should we finish

37:32.361 --> 37:34.501
the tofu puddings that are still intact?

37:34.881 --> 37:35.960
What are you saying?

37:35.961 --> 37:37.741
You guys can have the shattered ones.

37:37.961 --> 37:39.901
Deliver the intact ones to the manor.

37:41.321 --> 37:42.280
Amazing.

37:42.281 --> 37:43.821
You're killing two birds with one stone.

37:44.001 --> 37:46.520
Lu Ming delivered them to us?
Doesn't that mean

37:46.521 --> 37:48.101
they're from His Lordship?

37:49.241 --> 37:50.120
It's sweet, right?

37:50.121 --> 37:51.600
Mine is salty.

37:51.601 --> 37:53.320
Even so, it tastes sweet.

37:53.321 --> 37:54.701
Eat up.

37:55.081 --> 37:57.120
Even if it tastes salty,

37:57.121 --> 37:58.501
it's sweet in the heart.

38:27.401 --> 38:28.541
What flower is this?

38:28.551 --> 38:30.581
Fourth Young Lady,
why do you cherish it this much?

38:31.591 --> 38:33.421
I believe
that it can grow well independently.

38:34.001 --> 38:35.141
But I also believe

38:36.041 --> 38:37.661
that it can grow better

38:38.601 --> 38:40.061
with love and support.

38:46.521 --> 38:47.661
Ms. Longevity.

38:48.361 --> 38:50.621
Are you tending
to the plants by yourself?

38:50.961 --> 38:52.101
Grandmother.

38:59.121 --> 39:00.261
Ms. Longevity.

39:02.241 --> 39:03.880
If I were to stroll around

39:03.881 --> 39:06.301
the courtyard alone,

39:06.881 --> 39:08.501
I would also think about

39:08.841 --> 39:11.101
the person who plays the tune at night.

39:11.401 --> 39:12.861
Grandmother,

39:12.961 --> 39:14.341
what are you saying?

39:15.281 --> 39:16.120
I'm talking about

39:16.121 --> 39:18.341
the person on your mind right now.

39:19.841 --> 39:21.141
Let me ask you something.

39:22.641 --> 39:25.221
What was on your mind when Song Mo

39:25.361 --> 39:27.061
delivered the imperial decree to you?

39:27.081 --> 39:29.681
Grandmother, how did you know
that Song Mo delivered that to me?

39:30.641 --> 39:32.760
Do you think I'm ignorant just because

39:32.761 --> 39:34.421
I'm living at the manor?

39:35.491 --> 39:38.761
I have my own spies
in the Capital's Western Dou Family.

39:38.961 --> 39:40.101
Who are they?

39:40.681 --> 39:41.981
Don't shift the topic.

39:42.921 --> 39:43.960
Tell me

39:43.961 --> 39:45.541
what was on your mind.

39:49.041 --> 39:51.941
At first, when I heard it from him,

39:52.121 --> 39:53.741
I was shocked.

39:54.841 --> 39:57.141
I found it absolutely unbelievable.

39:57.921 --> 39:59.741
He and I were strangers,

40:00.121 --> 40:02.061
yet he did so much for me.

40:02.881 --> 40:04.941
I don't know how to repay him.

40:07.841 --> 40:11.421
You see, he begged His Majesty
for an imperial decree

40:11.901 --> 40:13.561
not for his own sake.

40:13.701 --> 40:15.801
He did it for your sake.

40:16.121 --> 40:18.721
He could've begged His Majesty
to grant him a marriage with you.

40:18.881 --> 40:21.120
However, he only begged His Majesty

40:21.121 --> 40:23.071
to grant you freedom
to decide your own marriage.

40:23.791 --> 40:26.941
I can see that he's sincere toward you.

40:28.501 --> 40:30.861
I can rest at ease

40:31.361 --> 40:33.301
now that a person like him
is watching over you.

40:40.281 --> 40:42.141
(Qianqing Palace)

40:42.241 --> 40:44.221
An insignificant marriage

40:44.641 --> 40:46.781
is actually stirring up a storm here.

40:47.281 --> 40:49.381
I've already given her
an imperial decree.

40:50.321 --> 40:54.661
Could it be that none of the men
in the Capital is good enough for her?

40:56.081 --> 40:57.301
Your Majesty,

40:57.441 --> 40:58.941
I've already promised my daughter

40:58.951 --> 41:00.881
that I would never interfere
with her marriage.

41:03.561 --> 41:04.701
Fine.

41:04.801 --> 41:06.661
Return to your residence
and make your choice.

41:06.801 --> 41:09.181
Don't return to the Ministry of Revenue
until you're done.

41:09.641 --> 41:11.181
Thank you, Your Majesty.

41:19.401 --> 41:20.500
Take a look!

41:20.501 --> 41:21.640
Take a look!

41:21.641 --> 41:24.221
Fresh vegetables for sale!

42:01.441 --> 42:02.581
Lord Dou,

42:03.001 --> 42:04.141
are you okay?

42:13.121 --> 42:14.621
(This is strange.)

42:14.631 --> 42:16.551
(He's actually sending me
back to my residence?)

42:16.601 --> 42:18.771
(My sworn enemy is helping me out now?)

42:18.901 --> 42:20.541
(What exactly is he up to?)

42:32.321 --> 42:33.240
(My goodness.)

42:33.241 --> 42:35.671
(Before this, I reprimanded
the Dou Family for being devious.)

42:35.681 --> 42:37.781
(But now, I'm the devious one.)

42:39.281 --> 42:41.341
(How can I change my image?)

42:56.441 --> 42:59.461
It seems like an explosion occurred
at a firecracker field on the outskirts.

42:59.761 --> 43:01.061
- Song Mo!
- Fourth Young Lady!

43:02.241 --> 43:03.880
Song Mo, I like you.

43:03.881 --> 43:05.441
I fear that I might lose you.

43:05.451 --> 43:07.000
You fear the seven reasons for divorce.

43:07.001 --> 43:08.971
Therefore, I'll write
the seven promises for you.

43:08.981 --> 43:11.650
I will respect all of your decisions
and ensure your safety.

43:11.651 --> 43:14.640
♪The dizziness of longing♪

43:14.641 --> 43:18.360
♪Like the sun
waiting for the flying wild geese♪

43:18.361 --> 43:21.751
♪The sound of weapons
chasing the long whip♪

43:22.241 --> 43:28.321
♪Never tired after a hundred battles,
because of you♪

43:28.631 --> 43:30.540
♪Morning and night, we meet again♪

43:30.541 --> 43:32.100
♪Walking slowly towards the distance♪

43:32.101 --> 43:35.471
♪Like leaves tangled in the wind,
tightly intertwined♪

43:35.511 --> 43:37.610
♪Together with you, wing to wing♪

43:37.611 --> 43:42.340
♪Our shadows flying,
dwelling together year after year♪

43:42.341 --> 43:44.120
♪Morning and night, with clear skies♪

43:44.121 --> 43:46.301
♪Clear wind and bright moon,
we wait for them♪

43:46.501 --> 43:49.120
♪Waiting for the fog to disperse
and the clouds to clear♪

43:49.121 --> 43:50.960
♪Tears that fall,
half a lifetime of tears♪

43:50.961 --> 43:55.361
♪Melted by your kiss,
melted by your kiss♪

43:55.901 --> 43:58.090
♪In this life, I wish to be like
Mandarin ducks in the water♪

43:58.091 --> 44:00.061
♪The green shore
is more beautiful than the sky♪

44:00.241 --> 44:02.890
♪The splendor
doesn't intoxicate the eyes♪

44:02.891 --> 44:04.620
♪Spring returns,
the swaying green lotus♪

44:04.621 --> 44:07.131
♪The mountains are distant,
what do I have to envy?

44:07.132 --> 44:09.640
♪Even so, I don't envy them♪

44:09.641 --> 44:11.850
♪In this life, I wish to
keep my promise to you♪

44:11.851 --> 44:14.030
♪Unchanged even to old age♪

44:14.031 --> 44:16.640
♪I will definitely
fulfill the promise without fail♪

44:16.641 --> 44:22.731
♪Seeing the full moon
even at the end of the world♪

44:31.001 --> 44:33.150
♪In this life, I wish to be like
Mandarin ducks in the water♪

44:33.151 --> 44:35.281
♪The green shore
is more beautiful than the sky♪

44:35.311 --> 44:37.930
♪The splendor
doesn't intoxicate the eyes♪

44:37.931 --> 44:39.620
♪Spring returns,
the swaying green lotus♪

44:39.621 --> 44:42.146
♪The mountains are distant,
what do I have to envy?

44:42.147 --> 44:44.670
♪Even so, I don't envy them♪

44:44.671 --> 44:46.750
♪In this life,
I wish to keep my promise to you♪

44:46.751 --> 44:48.961
♪Unchanged even to old age♪

44:48.991 --> 44:51.640
♪I will definitely
fulfill the promise without fail♪

44:51.641 --> 44:57.881
♪Seeing the full moon
even at the end of the world♪

45:01.881 --> 45:02.870
(No animals were harmed
in the making of this drama)

45:02.871 --> 45:03.850
(Every medical behaviour involved
and medicine used in the drama)

45:03.851 --> 45:05.101
(is required by the story.
Please don't try this at home)
